Dr. Nagy FARAG and Anne Marie, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
M K REAL ESTATE, LLC Farag, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-4997 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. December 27, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

Petitioners' petition to invoke the court's all writs jurisdiction and for writ of mandamus is denied.

KELLY, SLEET, and BADALAMENTI, JJ., Concur.
